### ── VIEWS ──────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Create view
POST http://localhost:3003/views
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "source": "mythicgames.com",
  "url": "/products/elden-ring",
  "visitor": "visitor-uuid-001",
  "createdAt": "2026-04-23T10:00:00Z",
  "meta": { "browser": "Chrome", "os": "Windows", "ref": "google" }
}

###
### Create another view
POST http://localhost:3003/views
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "source": "mythicgames.com",
  "url": "/products/witcher3",
  "visitor": "visitor-uuid-001",
  "createdAt": "2026-04-23T10:05:00Z",
  "meta": { "browser": "Chrome", "duration": 45 }
}

###
### Get all views
GET http://localhost:3003/views

###
### Get view by id (replace id)
GET http://localhost:3003/views/000000000000000000000001

### ── ACTIONS ─────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Create action
POST http://localhost:3003/actions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "source": "mythicgames.com",
  "url": "/products/elden-ring",
  "action": "add_to_cart",
  "visitor": "visitor-uuid-001",
  "createdAt": "2026-04-23T10:02:00Z",
  "meta": { "productId": "abc123", "price": 49.99 }
}

###
### Create another action
POST http://localhost:3003/actions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "source": "mythicgames.com",
  "url": "/checkout",
  "action": "checkout_start",
  "visitor": "visitor-uuid-001",
  "createdAt": "2026-04-23T10:08:00Z",
  "meta": { "cartTotal": 49.99 }
}

###
### Get all actions
GET http://localhost:3003/actions

### ── GOALS ───────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Create goal
POST http://localhost:3003/goals
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "source": "mythicgames.com",
  "url": "/checkout/success",
  "goal": "purchase_complete",
  "visitor": "visitor-uuid-001",
  "createdAt": "2026-04-23T10:12:00Z",
  "meta": { "orderId": "ord-999", "total": 49.99, "currency": "EUR" }
}

###
### Get all goals
GET http://localhost:3003/goals

###
### Get goal details with visitor journey (replace id)
GET http://localhost:3003/goals/GOAL_ID_HERE/details

### ── PATCH / DELETE ──────────────────────────────────────────

### Patch a view
PATCH http://localhost:3003/views/VIEW_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{ "meta": { "browser": "Firefox", "updated": true } }

###
### Delete a view
DELETE http://localhost:3003/views/VIEW_ID_HERE
